<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ry Tompo ô, tahio
 Izao dianay izao ;
 Ny lehibe ampio,
 Ny kely mba tezao.
 Fa ny Anaranao
 No iaingana anio ;
 Tantano sy vimbino
 An-dalana izahay.</lyrics>
<title>Ry Tompo o, tahio FFPM716</title>
<author>G.J. Webb</author>
<hymn_number>716</hymn_number>
</song>